{"word":"H5676 - עֵבֶר - ʻêber - ay'-ber - [idiom] against","slug":"H5676","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עֵבֶר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻêber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ay'-ber"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] against"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D1;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;e&#x0302;ber</b> - <i>ay'-ber</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5674\">H5674</a>; properly a region <i>across</i>; but used only adverbially (with or without a preposition) on the <i>opposite</i> side (especially of the Jordan; usually meaning the <i>east</i>): -  X against, beyond, by, X from, over, passage, quarter, (other, this) side, straight."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4569\">H4569</a>, <a href=\"#/H5668\">H5668</a>, <a href=\"#/H5669\">H5669</a>, <a href=\"#/H5674\">H5674</a>, <a href=\"#/H5677\">H5677</a>, <a href=\"#/H5678\">H5678</a>, <a href=\"#/H5679\">H5679</a>, <a href=\"#/H5680\">H5680</a>, <a href=\"#/H5681\">H5681</a>, <a href=\"#/H5682\">H5682</a>, <a href=\"#/H5683\">H5683</a>, <a href=\"#/H5684\">H5684</a>"}]}